    "News from Vancleare I Women RLDS Hold Meet By MRS RAY HAVENS Dinner guests Monday of Mrs Hettie Ware were the Rev and Ms Binford Smith the Rev Jack Waldrop Mrs Jack Flet cher and Miss Forrest Nell Flet cher Hie Rev Waldrop is hold ing a revival at the Mount Pleasant church this week The leaders training meeting of the officials of the two womens divisions of the RLDS Church met at the church Monday morning with Mrs Coleen McMillan head leader in charge There were around ten present Mrs Beadie Russum who has been in the hospital in Laurel re turned to the home of Nolle T Roberts where she has been re siding Sunday she was accom panied here by Mr and Mrs Bill Cochran of Florida Mrs Faye Sellers gave her dau ghter Annette a party on her sixth birthday Friday Attending were Jeanie and Kennie Inabi Bette Bob Quave Tutu Goff Cathy Mattingly Carlie Seymour David Entrekin Tippy Ladner and Debbie Quave Aka Roberts who has been visiting Us grandparents Mr and Un L G Roberts left Sun i 4 BIB LEAGUE GAME OF THE WEEK Erj Satefef l Slay WALATV CHANNEL 10 Cosponsored by"
